title: Emma Roche stuns at the launch of Kendall Jenner's new hair range
text:
Last week she confirmed that she was single and looking for love.

And on Thursday, The Bachelor star Emma Roche stunned in a plunging sleeveless dress as she attended the launch of Kendall Jenner's new hair tools range in Sydney.

The 32-year-old was a vision in a navy blue and black dress.

Single stunner! The Bachelor's Emma Roche stunned in plunging sleeveless dress at the launch of Kendall Jenner's new hair tools range in Sydney on Thursday

The reality star, who failed to find love with Matt Agnew on The Bachelor, looked dazzling in oversized hoop earrings.

She opted for minimal makeup, wearing a light shade of foundation, coral lip gloss and black mascara.

Emma completed the look with manicured white acrylic nails and a series of gold chains around her neck.

Chic: She opted for minimal makeup, wearing a light shade of foundation and lip gloss

The brand manager was joined by fellow Australian model Lauren Vickers who looked chic in a white laced top.

Last week, Emma slammed reports that she was dating Married at First Sight villain Dean Wells after the pair were photographed together.

Speaking to Now to Love on Friday, The Bachelor star insisted that there's nothing more than friendship between herself and the reality TV bad boy.

'I'm still single and looking for love': The Bachelor's Emma Roche shut down rumours that she's dating Married At First Sight's Dean Wells

All right in white! The brand mnaager was joined by fellow Australian model Lauren Vickers who looked chic in a white laced top

'We are just good friends but there's nothing romantic there,' she told the publication.

The 32-year-old added: 'I'm still single and looking for love.'

Dean shocked fans on Wednesday, last week after he uploaded a photo of himself looking cosy with Emma at an event, leading people to believe that the pair were an item.

However, the following day he shut down the rumours following a flurry of media articles.
description: Last week she confirmed that she was single and looking for love.
authors: Ali Daher For Daily Mail Australia
